no_action\",\n  \"summary\": \"No extra setup is required: maven-core 2.0.7 is a plain Java Maven core artifact with its required compile/runtime dependencies declared transitively, and the reported failure is caused by generated tests using outdated maven-artifact exception constructor signatures rather than by missing dependencies, Docker services, or environment/system properties.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Tests that invoke MavenCli for real project execution may touch user.dir, user.home, settings.xml, and the local Maven repository; if such tests are generated, they should isolate those paths in test code, but this is not required as pre-generation setup.\",\n    \"Existing 2.0.6 tests must be adjusted for 2.0.7 API signatures, especially ArtifactResolutionException and ArtifactNotFoundException constructors.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_078d2096c8509891016a4181b3091881959f8e07bc6e5ac5cf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1250, "output": 711, "cacheRead": 23552, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 25513, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782677928882, "responseId": "resp_078d2096c8509891016a4181a954a88195809f2fd3c7a1815e"}, "toolResults": []}
